<div class="page" id="page-story">

  <div style="padding-top: 80px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--stone), var(--charcoal));">
    <div class="page-hero">
      <div>
        <span class="page-hero-label">Who We Are</span>
        <h1 class="page-hero-title">Our Story</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="story-page">

    <div class="story-block reveal">
      <span class="label">The Beginning</span>
      <h2>Born from an obsession with time.</h2>
      <p>ERAZ did not begin in a design studio or a boardroom. It began with a question asked late at night, staring at images of cave paintings in Altamira — <strong>what if we still wore these stories?</strong></p>
      <p>Every civilisation that ever existed left behind a visual language. Symbols carved into rock. Geometric patterns beaten into bronze. Laurel wreaths pressed into marble. Heraldic crests stitched into banners. These were not just decorations — they were identity. They said: <em>I was here. This is what I believed. This is what I fought for.</em></p>
      <p>ERAZ is our answer to that question. We are a clothing brand built on the conviction that history's visual languages are too powerful, too beautiful, and too human to be left in museums.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="story-divider"></div>

    <div class="story-quote reveal">
      <p>"Every piece we make is a translation. We take something ancient and ask: what does it mean to wear this today?"</p>
    </div>

    <div class="story-block reveal">
      <span class="label">The Philosophy</span>
      <h2>History is not a museum. It is a wardrobe.</h2>
      <p>We believe clothing is the most personal archive a human being can carry. What you wear tells the story of who you are, where you come from, and what you value. ERAZ exists to make that story richer — to connect you, through cloth and thread, to the thousands of years of human creativity that came before you.</p>
      <p>We are not a nostalgia brand. We are not a heritage brand in the traditional sense. We are a <strong>translation studio</strong> — taking the visual vocabulary of ancient civilisations and building it into garments that belong in the present moment, on the streets of Lahore, Karachi, and Islamabad.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="story-divider"></div>

    <div class="story-block reveal">
      <span class="label">Our Values</span>
      <h2>What we stand for.</h2>
      <div class="story-values">
        <div class="story-value">
          <div class="story-value-icon">📜</div>
          <h4 class="story-value-title">Authenticity</h4>
          <p class="story-value-desc">Every motif is researched. Every pattern is sourced from real historical records, not invented aesthetics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-value">
          <div class="story-value-icon">🧵</div>
          <h4 class="story-value-title">Craft</h4>
          <p class="story-value-desc">We refuse shortcuts. Every garment is made to be worn, washed, and passed down — not discarded after a season.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-value">
          <div class="story-value-icon">🌍</div>
          <h4 class="story-value-title">Belonging</h4>
          <p class="story-value-desc">History belongs to everyone. Our collections draw from civilisations across every continent and culture.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story-divider"></div>

    <div class="story-block reveal" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>Ready to wear history?</h2>
